{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Stop Religious Education (RE) being compulsory in English schools from Year 10",
        "additional_details": "Many schools make RE a compulsory GCSE. We believe children who are not interested in RE could have more choice and time to spend on subjects that they are interested in. A 2023 Ofsted reports showed that the quality of Religious Education in schools was of poor quality.",
        "background": "We urge the Government to stop making Religious Education (RE) compulsory in schools in England, and to allow it to be an optional subject from Year 10 onwards.",
